   <abstract>This recto has an advertisement for the Montana Slim, which is a list of thirty-five songs written and composed by Wilf Carter. The recto also shows Wilf Carter sitting down, holding a cigarette and a guitar. Recto reads: Keep Smiling Wilf Carter. Verso reads: Hello there, Sure glad you enjoy my Radio programs I want your to know your letters make me feel happy, and that I read and answer everyone personally. Hope you like this little card and believe me would sure appreciate an answer to this card address all mail to WABC New York City, N.Y.. Addressed to Hazel Fuller.</abstract>
